[CS:GO Version!](http://gamebanana.com/csgo/maps/171364 "Click Me! =)") ======================================================================= About the map: ============== **-Lots of brush work in making the crates, arches, the tower, etc.**
**-Waterfall texture used, HQ lego textures used, and HDR Lighting used.**
**-16 Terrorists Spawn and 16 Counter-Terrorists Spawn.**
**-Crates here and there for cover.**
**-3 Storey tower with a roof.**
Credits: ======== **Matr!X7689** - Basic designing from scratch and lots of brush work.
**Minerr** - Tweaks and brush work, also the Green water texture.
**RaZZer App** - Green water texture base.
**TopHattWaffle** - Green waterfall.
**Digital Assassin** - HQ lego textures using normal maps.
If any issues/queries, contact me. ---------------------------------- ### -Hope you like it! ### -Darkside Studios
